/*

CC 48: Filter Resonance
CC 49: Filter Cutoff
CC 50: LFO Frequency
CC 51: LFO Level
CC 52: Filter Envelope Amount
CC 53: Portamento
CC 54: Pulse Width/PWM Rate
CC 55: Oscillator Detune
CC 58: Filter Decay
CC 59: Filter Attack
CC 60: Amplitude Decay
CC 61: Amplitude Attack

http://meeblip.com/use-one/micro-kit-assembly/

*/

